message.body: Can only do a short walk tonight (have to finish a paper) but looking forward to it! What time is good?
Does 6 work? I'm certainly in need I some fresh air!
Yup! I'll meet you at your place
Sounds good. Or we can swing by to get you. We can walk around the prison and possibly the art museum if u have time.
Hmm, OK. Then yeah, text when you're outside my place! also: want to go to the Phillies game next Wednesday? :)
Me? At a Phil's game. Sure! As long as u don't mind explaining everything about baseball.
I do not mind that at all :) I know it's not as good as a flyers game, but I have nice seats in left center field
Are u kidding?! That's awesome. I can't tell u how long it has been since I've been to a baseball game. Thanks!
Just got home. We'll be over by 6:15. Sorry.
I got a pair of ASICS off the clearance rack! They feel super comfy. I hope they work out.
Awesome! That must be a record for the quickest shoe buying experience!
I told the guy it was my quickest buying experience for anything in history. I only had to try on two pairs!
